<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>climb.mx</title>
  
  <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="description" content="<%= meta_description(nil, "Hi, I'm Everardo, a high energy individual focused on creative product development, art and long distance cycling.") %>">
  
  <!-- Open Graph Tags for social media sharing -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="climb.mx">
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= meta_description(nil, "Hi, I'm Everardo, a high energy individual focused on creative product development, art and long distance cycling.") %>">
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= og_url %>">
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= og_image_url %>">
  
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      color: #666666;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .ascii-art {
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      white-space: pre;
      margin: 40px 0;
      color: #999999;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: normal;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 30px 0 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    
    .nav {
      margin: 40px 0;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .nav a {
      color: #666666;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    
    .nav a:hover {
      color: #333333;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .content {
      margin: 40px 0;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: normal;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .content p {
      margin: 15px 0;
      color: #666666;
    }
    
    .content ul {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .content li {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #666666;
    }
    
    .email-signup {
      margin: 40px 0;
      padding: 30px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .email-signup h3 {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: normal;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .email-signup p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    
    .email-signup input[type="email"] {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      margin: 0 5px;
      border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      color: #333333;
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      width: 200px;
    }
    
    .email-signup button {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      color: #666666;
      border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    
    .email-signup button:hover {
      background: #F5F5F5;
      color: #333333;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #999999;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container"> 
    <div class="title">climb.mx</div>
    
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="/posts">posts</a>
      <a href="/about">about</a>
      <a href="/contact">contact</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi, I'm Everardo, a high energy individual focused on creative product development, art and long distance cycling.</p>
      
      <h2>recent posts</h2>
      
      <% posts = Post.all.first(7) %>
      <% if posts.any? %>
        <ul>
          <% posts.each do |post| %>
            <li><a href="/posts/<%= post.slug %>" style="color: #666666; text-decoration: none;"><%= post.title %></a></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      <% else %>
        <ul>
          <li>coming soon: Something is wrong, please let me know</li>
          <li>coming soon: Blog posts should appear here</li>
        </ul>
      <% end %>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999999; font-size: 12px;">
        This blog is FOSS and you can find the source code on <a href="https://github.com/ebarojas/ror.climb.mx">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-signup">
      <h3>newsletter-ish</h3>
      <p>I don't use social media, so if you want to get updates from me every now and then, leave your email.</p>
      <form id="email-form">
        <input type="email" id="email-input" name="email" placeholder="correo@servidor.com.mx" required>
        <button type="button" onclick="goToSubscribe()">go!</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    
    <script>
      function goToSubscribe() {
        var email = document.getElementById('email-input').value;
        if (email) {
          window.location.href = '/subscribe?email=' + encodeURIComponent(email);
        } else {
          window.location.href = '/subscribe';
        }
      }
    </script>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2025 climb.mx</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 